Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.62,0:00:03.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们尸鬼 以人为食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:05.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到夏野死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:10.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节子和干康也是那副样子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:14.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到讨厌的家伙遭罪 真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:19.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:21.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:22.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:23.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:47.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.16,0:00:53.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:01:01.11,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}朝の光を手放した花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:01:01.11,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}舍弃晨曦之花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:04.63,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}注がれない雨を求め
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:04.63,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}渴求不会降临的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:11.61,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}覚めない眠りにつく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:11.61,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}沉睡于永不觉醒的长眠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:23.91,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰かをそっと呼ぶ声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:23.91,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}轻声呼唤着谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:25.16,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闇の楽園は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:25.16,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}暗夜的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:26.90,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嘘か夢か
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:26.90,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是梦是幻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:28.90,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}失うのは身体と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:28.90,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs14\pos(345,330)}カラダ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:28.90,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}失去的是身体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.97,0:01:30.47,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}自分という心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.97,0:01:30.47,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}和自我之心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.26,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その対価を差し出し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.26,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}付出如此代价
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:35.33,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}何を得られるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:35.33,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}又能得到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:39.09,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}この涙で奪える程に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:39.09,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}连这泪水都能将之夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:42.41,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}命は脆くて儚くて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:42.41,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}生命脆弱而飘忽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:45.88,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全てに訪れる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:45.88,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}当一切造访
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:49.21,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}死を「恐怖」と嘆くのか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:49.21,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs14\pos(235,330)}終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:49.21,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要将死亡叹作恐怖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:52.87,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終演を歌う金盞花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:52.87,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}鸣唱终演的金盏花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:56.20,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}静かに咲き誇る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:56.20,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}静静绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:57.88,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}憎しみも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:57.88,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}将憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:01:59.61,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲しみも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:01:59.61,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:03.16,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その根でたくり寄せて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:03.16,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全部寄于根茎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:06.62,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終焉を歌う金盞花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:06.62,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}鸣唱终焉的金盏花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:09.91,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}寂しさを潤す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:09.91,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}渴求滋润孤寂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:13.44,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}注がれない雨を求めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:13.44,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那不会降临的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:19.45,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}覚めない眠りにつく
